com.azure.core.amqp.exception

Enum ErrorCondition

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ErrorCondition>
      • com.azure.core.amqp.exception.ErrorCondition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ErrorCondition>

    public enum ErrorCondition
extends Enum<ErrorCondition>
    Contains constants common to the AMQP protocol and constants shared by Azure services.
    See Also:
    AMQP 1.0: Transport Errors, Azure Messaging Exceptions
